text: Wang Yanan (born 8 September 1991) is a Chinese female Paralympic sitting volleyball player. She is part of the China women's national sitting volleyball team. She competed at the 2012 Summer Paralympics winning the gold medal, and 2016 Summer Paralympics winning the silver medal. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese sitting volleyball players Category:Paralympic gold medalists for China Category:Paralympic silver medalists for China
